1
00:01:38,888 --> 00:01:46,888
<i>[Bad for Bad]</i>

2
00:02:47,449 --> 00:02:48,991
Did you steal my money?

3
00:02:52,449 --> 00:02:54,449
You could've just asked nicely.

4
00:02:57,991 --> 00:02:59,491
If I asked you nicely,

5
00:03:00,407 --> 00:03:01,866
you'd only give me a grand or two.

6
00:03:03,074 --> 00:03:05,407
Just taking it gets me way more.

7
00:03:08,824 --> 00:03:10,157
Why are you hiding the money?

8
00:03:15,361 --> 00:03:16,569
I...

9
00:03:17,903 --> 00:03:19,236
was saving it for us to use,

10
00:03:20,194 --> 00:03:23,194
for when Jae Chu kicks you out.

11
00:03:24,611 --> 00:03:25,736
Is that so?

12
00:03:28,069 --> 00:03:29,194
Nong,

13
00:03:29,653 --> 00:03:31,194
can I ask you for one thing?

14
00:03:31,694 --> 00:03:33,111
Just this one thing.

15
00:03:37,194 --> 00:03:39,194
You can be awful to anyone else,

16
00:03:40,194 --> 00:03:41,569
but don't be awful to me, okay?

17
00:03:42,403 --> 00:03:43,444
I'm begging you.

18
00:03:46,611 --> 00:03:47,694
I don't know.

19
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:51,611
If you love me, I'll love you back.

20
00:03:57,944 --> 00:04:00,194
But if you're awful to me,

21
00:04:01,069 --> 00:04:02,569
I'll be awful right back.

22
00:04:03,194 --> 00:04:05,236
I'm not a complicated person.

23
00:04:47,839 --> 00:04:48,923
Hey.

24
00:04:51,006 --> 00:04:53,256
If he sees our faces, it's trouble.

25
00:04:53,673 --> 00:04:54,839
Why are you scared of him?

26
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,506
A guy like him won't mess with us.

27
00:04:56,506 --> 00:04:58,964
I already threatened him.
If you don't believe me, follow me.

28
00:05:22,763 --> 00:05:24,304
You remember what I said, right?

29
00:05:25,554 --> 00:05:27,763
If you tell anyone about us,

30
00:05:29,304 --> 00:05:30,554
you're dead.

31
00:05:36,304 --> 00:05:38,304
Everything is karma.

32
00:05:39,096 --> 00:05:41,638
For us, it's already over.

33
00:05:43,179 --> 00:05:45,888
Over since the day you two did that

34
00:05:47,554 --> 00:05:49,846
to us, and to the person...

35
00:05:53,221 --> 00:05:54,346
I love.

36
00:05:56,888 --> 00:05:58,054
It's good you think that way.

37
00:05:58,763 --> 00:06:00,388
Vengeance ends when you stop
seeking it.

38
00:06:02,804 --> 00:06:04,013
Listen to me carefully, Nong.

39
00:06:07,304 --> 00:06:08,763
Whoever crossed me,

40
00:06:10,013 --> 00:06:11,846
I'll make them pay
to the very end.

41
00:06:12,763 --> 00:06:14,888
That's your business, why tell me?

42
00:07:06,933 --> 00:07:08,600
Honestly, I feel bad for Shane.

43
00:07:09,350 --> 00:07:11,350
His relationship was going so well,

44
00:07:11,683 --> 00:07:13,558
and his boyfriend died
because of your temper.

45
00:07:14,808 --> 00:07:16,350
It's all karma.

46
00:07:16,850 --> 00:07:18,517
Didn't you hear what Shane said?

47
00:07:28,100 --> 00:07:29,558
What the...?

48
00:07:34,815 --> 00:07:35,815
Hey,

49
00:07:36,231 --> 00:07:37,273
I remember now.

50
00:07:38,690 --> 00:07:40,690
This is Shane's boyfriend's ring.

51
00:07:41,773 --> 00:07:42,773
Really?

52
00:07:45,023 --> 00:07:46,398
Should we go sell it?

53
00:07:46,398 --> 00:07:48,398
We really need the cash right now.

54
00:07:48,398 --> 00:07:50,398
A ring like this won't fetch much.

55
00:07:51,398 --> 00:07:52,815
Let me add some value to it.

56
00:07:53,898 --> 00:07:56,398
Here's the plan. I'll wait at home.

57
00:07:56,398 --> 00:07:58,398
You go lure Shane in.

58
00:07:59,773 --> 00:08:01,398
I'll film us gang-raping him,

59
00:08:03,106 --> 00:08:05,106
and then we sell it. Sound good?

60
00:08:06,231 --> 00:08:07,898
We get the content,

61
00:08:08,315 --> 00:08:10,023
and we get his body too.

62
00:08:10,398 --> 00:08:11,565
Good...

63
00:08:11,690 --> 00:08:12,773
So go wait at the house.

64
00:08:12,773 --> 00:08:13,898
Good.

65
00:08:44,033 --> 00:08:45,158
Hey,

66
00:08:46,074 --> 00:08:48,658
if you want the ring, follow me.

67
00:08:51,991 --> 00:08:53,991
You have Nat's ring?

68
00:08:55,241 --> 00:08:56,283
Yeah.

69
00:08:56,991 --> 00:08:58,158
If you don't believe me

70
00:08:58,658 --> 00:08:59,866
and don't follow me,

71
00:09:00,408 --> 00:09:01,533
I guess you don't want it.

72
00:09:03,908 --> 00:09:05,116
Promise me first

73
00:09:05,449 --> 00:09:08,199
that if I go, you'll return it.

74
00:09:09,574 --> 00:09:11,574
Of course. I'll give it back.

75
00:09:12,574 --> 00:09:13,991
Don't stall.

76
00:09:14,033 --> 00:09:15,949
If Krit sells your ring for food,

77
00:09:16,866 --> 00:09:18,491
I can't help you anymore.

78
00:09:42,062 --> 00:09:46,642
Just keep walking, hey!
